data.description: Don't miss out on this great home....FABULOUS thoughtful design makes this low-maintenance home a beauty. This spectacular home sits within walking distance to the Marietta square. Only a few years old, it is charming to say the least. Hedges Park is situated within minutes of Historic Downtown Marietta.  Escape, gather, and refresh your senses with music, food and festivals.  Meandering sidewalks for a stroll or walking your dogs.  Inside this 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath home you'll find, hardwood flooring throughout main level and upgraded tile throughout. The Kitchen has an open flow which is great for entertaining. Stainless-steel appliances, beautiful gray, double stack cabinetry, custom built pantry and large island which is perfect for hosting dinner parties and holidays gatherings. For your convenience a powder bath is situated right off the kitchen. As you enter the main level you will love how it opens to the family room with tons of windows with an abundance of natural light. Wake up to gorgeous, tranquil views through the windows in the owner's suite. The primary bathroom has a magnificent, large walk-in shower that includes upgraded large tiles. The double vanity stretches from wall to wall with tons of counter space and added storage. Spacious walk-In closet that has been designed to organize all your clothes, shoes, handbags and ties.  A few features not to be missed include 4.5" plantation shutters throughout. In addition, all bedroom closets have been custom designed to include the kitchen pantry, laundry room and linen closet. Tiled bathroom flooring throughout.  Custom keeping area sits right inside the back door off the garage.  Finally, you will love the large outdoor porch to enjoy on warm summer nights or cool crisp fall nights. This home has been meticulously maintained, better than new.  Just a one mile walk or golf cart ride via Mountain-to-River Trail to Downtown Marietta.  Come enjoy the lifestyle and all it has to offer: concerts, breweries, shopping, weekend markets and restaurants. Just a few minutes stroll to the new coffee shop and retail stores. Location, Location, Location!
